<bibRefCitation author="BUCK, M. &amp; MARSHALL, S. A." pageId="11" pageNumber="236" pagination="1 - 139" refId="ref14746" refString="BUCK, M. &amp; MARSHALL, S. A. (2009) Revision of New World Leptocera Olivier (Diptera, Sphaeroceridae). Zootaxa 2039: 1 - 139." type="journal article" year="2009">BUCK and MARSHALL (2009)</bibRefCitation>
